      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a really strong start. i like how you framed it as an \"essential economic lever\". \n\ncan you expand on that part about the \"historical theft\"? i want to make sure the essay doesn't just sound like a wish list but actually explains why the current system is fundamentally broken or unjust compared to something like meritocracy. like, how do i frame meritocracy as being kind of a myth in this context?",
